result.name: BALCONY

reviews.text: Shisha flavour was good..considering the price is quite cheap
Nice and chill, good place for gathering.
Quite comfortable and cozy for a Saturday evening.  Enjoyable music that is not too loud for chit chat.  Slight improvement on their drinks menu (especially beers) would make this a better place.

Next to Regal Hotel, served draft beer. Have a small balcony upstairs with live band playing music 🎶 around 11:00. I was there on Sat. Not sure if they had live band on weekday night. 

While they had issue of mosquito, me and my fd both suffer from mosquito bite. Ask for the mosquito spray if required from The bartender.
Nice bar for chill w live music n frdly services.
